{"tid":661141,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【沈振盈 - 實戰理論】純技術反彈 挾淡倉而已","createTime":"2018-05-11T09:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T10:35:56.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99dc6fbb03aff267cff0cdf7889b368870ddc490","tid":661141,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"【實戰理論】純技術反彈 挾淡倉而已（沈振盈）（MAY 11）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.winmoney.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.winmoney.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BD%2588.png&h=ce308f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美股連升多日，道指重上24700點，港股亦在騰訊（<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cd113be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>）及油股的帶動下，從低位回升逾1000點，昨晚美國港股ADR亦升上31100點水平。若配合昨晚外圍市況的表現，加上牛熊証街貨的比例，看來今日港股會裂口高開殺熊。<br />\n<br />\n若撇除衍生工具殺倉因素，基本面沒有太大改變，技術上仍然維持上落市格局。後市大方向，當然仍受到加息步伐、債息上升、美元強勢及中美貿易戰等因素影響。但短線方面，則仍是市場情緒所主導，而市場大戶有着控制市場情緒的能力，自然可以將大市舞高弄低，好淡皆殺。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊下週公佈業績，股價從低位375.4元急速反彈至406元，彈升速度驚人。此一波的回升，也是可以理解，皆因市場不少散戶仍對其股價有憧憬，只要反彈訊號一現，自然能夠一呼百應。問題在於，業績前股價已大幅回升，高追的風險已極高。而且，筆者預期其第一季的盈利表現，會進一步顯示，核心業務增長放緩。故此，公佈前炒定上去，點計條數都不應該再追。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.winmoney.hk/famous/%E3%80%90%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96%E3%80%91%E7%B4%94%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-%E6%8C%BE%E6%B7%A1%E5%80%89%E8%80%8C%E5%B7%B2%EF%BC%88%E6%B2%88%E6%8C%AF%E7%9B%88%EF%BC%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.winmoney.hk%2Ffamous%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25AB%2596%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%258C%25BE%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E5%2580%2589%25E8%2580%258C%25E5%25B7%25B2%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%25B2%2588%25E6%258C%25AF%25E7%259B%2588%25EF%25BC%2589%2F&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=aabcccb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.winmoney.hk/famous/%E3%80%90%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96%E3%80%91%E7%B4%94%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-%E6%8C%BE%E6%B7%A1%E5%80%89%E8%80%8C%E5%B7%B2%EF%BC%88%E6%B2%88%E6%8C%AF%E7%9B%88%EF%BC%89/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家不應再追貨, 回頭是岸開熊才是王道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3181b61d5f1a466ff42af804a9b62eeeeb482f4d","tid":661141,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"夜期又做世界，有冇人幫手沽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c61bf22e42da108f1cf6d999457e415a4f084ed","tid":661141,"uid":54895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"大師今年幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}